{"word":"βασανίζω","slug":"βασανίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βασανίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάσανος\">βάσανος</a></el>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prim.\">prim.</a> ‘rub upon the touchstone’, then ‘examine closely’, ‘torture’] ‘subject to severe distress’, <b><i>afflict, torment, torture</i> <a href='B:470 8:6'>Mt 8:6</a>, <a href='B:470 8:29'>29</a>; <a href='B:480 5:7'>Mk 5:7</a>; <a href='B:490 8:28'>Lk 8:28</a>; <a href='B:680 2:8'>2 Pt 2:8</a>; <a href='B:730 9:5'>Rv 9:5</a>; <a href='B:730 11:10'>11:10</a>; <a href='B:730 12:2'>12:2</a>; <a href='B:730 14:10'>14:10</a>; <a href='B:730 20:10'>20:10</a>.</b> Of a boat or sailors experiencing adverse weather conditions, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b><i>labor</i> <a href='B:470 14:24'>Mt 14:24</a>; <a href='B:480 6:48'>Mk 6:48</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βαρύτιμος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βασανισμός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}